<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạnạ mhmạ bʿdt</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạnạ mhmạ bʿdt hạfḍl mkạny hnạ
 nzʿl wngẖḍb wfy ywm ntṣạlḥ klnạ
 tfḍl mḥbẗ ạsạshạ wạḥd ḥbnạ
 mḥbẗ tkfy tmlạ qlwbnạ klnạ
 bkrẗ ạlnhạrdh wyʿdy ywm bʿd ywm
 qlwbnạ wạḥdh wbynạ ḥb yzyd wydwm</lyrics>
